# AI Invoice Generator

An automated workflow that generates and emails professional invoices from a single form submission.

## What it does
- Receives invoice details via webhook (client name, email, service, amount)
- Uses AI to generate a clean, professional HTML invoice with inline styling
- Auto-generates invoice number and date, sets a 30-day due date
- Emails the finished invoice directly to the client, ready to print or save as PDF

## Why it matters
Manual invoicing is slow and error-prone. This system turns a quick form entry into a polished, client-ready invoice delivered instantly by email — no templates, no formatting, no copy-paste.

## Built with
n8n · AI (Groq / Llama) · Gmail · Webhooks

